<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Non-Disclosure Agreement</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #2c3e50; }
      .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .section-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }
      .signature-block {
        margin-top: 50px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .signature { width: 45%; }
      .signature-line {
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT</h1>
      <p>Between {{employerName}} and {{employeeName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>CONTRACT REFERENCE</div>
      <p>Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
      <p>Date of Issue: {{issueDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>1. PARTIES</div>
      <p><strong>Disclosing Party (Employer):</strong>
        {{employerName}}<br />
        Address: {{employerAddress}}<br />
        Email: {{employerEmail}}</p>
      <p><strong>Receiving Party (Employee):</strong>
        {{employeeName}}<br />
        Address: {{employeeAddress}}<br />
        Email: {{employeeEmail}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>2. PURPOSE</div>
      <p>In connection with the Employee's engagement as <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong>
        commencing <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>, the Disclosing Party may share
        confidential information with the Receiving Party. This Agreement governs
        the handling of such information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>3. DEFINITION OF CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION</div>
      <p>"Confidential Information" means any non-public information disclosed by
        the Employer, including but not limited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business plans, strategies, and financial data</li>
        <li>Client and customer lists, contacts, and data</li>
        <li>Trade secrets, proprietary processes, and methodologies</li>
        <li>Software, source code, and technical documentation</li>
        <li>Product designs, prototypes, and research</li>
        <li>Employee and salary information</li>
        <li>Any other information designated as confidential</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>4. OBLIGATIONS</div>
      <p>The Receiving Party agrees to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hold all Confidential Information in strict confidence</li>
        <li>Not disclose Confidential Information to any third party without prior written consent</li>
        <li>Use Confidential Information solely for the purposes of their employment</li>
        <li>Apply at least the same level of protection as they apply to their own confidential information</li>
        <li>Immediately notify the Employer upon discovering any unauthorised disclosure</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>5. EXCLUSIONS</div>
      <p>Confidential Information does not include information that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Is or becomes publicly known through no breach of this Agreement</li>
        <li>Was rightfully known by the Receiving Party prior to disclosure</li>
        <li>Is required to be disclosed by law or court order</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>6. DURATION</div>
      <p>The obligations under this Agreement remain in effect during the
        term of employment and for a period of <strong>two (2) years</strong>
        after termination of employment, regardless of reason.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>7. RETURN OF INFORMATION</div>
      <p>Upon termination of employment or upon request, the Receiving Party
        shall promptly return or destroy all materials containing Confidential
        Information, including any copies or summaries.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>8. REMEDIES</div>
      <p>The Receiving Party acknowledges that breach of this Agreement may
        cause irreparable harm for which monetary damages would be inadequate.
        The Employer is therefore entitled to seek injunctive relief in addition
        to all other remedies available at law or in equity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>9. GOVERNING LAW</div>
      <p>This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the Federal Republic
        of Nigeria.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='signature-block'>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Employer Signature</strong><br />
          Name: {{employerName}}<br />
          {{#if employerSignedAt}}
            Date: {{employerSignedAt}}<br />
            IP: {{employerSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Employee Signature</strong><br />
          Name: {{employeeName}}<br />
          {{#if employeeSignedAt}}
            Date: {{employeeSignedAt}}<br />
            IP: {{employeeSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Contract processed through JobStack Talent Solutions</p>
      <p>This is a legally binding document. Please read carefully before signing.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
